00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:31.600
Lesson 1

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:33.060
"When exchanging business cards"

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:37.240
In business society, exchanging business cards is inevitable.

00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:39.720
The most important thing during a business card exchange is...

00:00:39.940 --> 00:00:42.260
Height of your business card when exchanging cards!

00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:44.480
If someone has a higher position,

00:00:44.740 --> 00:00:46.740
let them introduce first.

00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:47.880
And then,

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.620
Do not take their until they receive my business card first.

00:00:50.660 --> 00:00:52.060
Did everyone know?

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.040
With an exception,

00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:55.180
There will be a problem here.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:58.420
For example,  a situation when both party doesn't know the position of the other person.

00:00:58.520 --> 00:01:01.140
If they think they're inferior than the other,...

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:03.420
That's how the business card exchange begin.

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:04.540
It's to fight. (determine who's first)

00:01:04.580 --> 00:01:07.100
