00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:45.900
Lesson 2

00:01:45.940 --> 00:01:46.980
"When toasting"

00:01:47.140 --> 00:01:49.140
Just like with the business card exchange before,

00:01:49.140 --> 00:01:51.600
